{"tid":1223972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就算情況再差 不撤不散！","createTime":"2019-06-15T00:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T04:13:18.000Z","uid":178933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"241eb4f77e9aae33074a49b8e24586f951dd799c","tid":1223972,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:46:27.000Z","msg":"喱一刻 你或者覺得好無助 無力 心累<br />\n好似做咩都徒勞無功<br />\n明明已經好努力 但前面嘅路仲係好灰暗<br />\n我明 大家都累 都想停低 唔想再行<br />\n但係你記住你唔係一個人 <br />\n一路上 都係同路人 <br />\n受左傷都忍住痛繼續向前行<br />\n為左移除障礙唔介意跑慢幾步<br />\n就算好驚好細膽都願意行前多一步嘅人<br />\n甚至有好多願意回頭再拉你一把嘅人<br />\n佢地無選擇停低 退後<br />\n因為佢地知道<br />\n守護屋企重要嘅價值比一切重要<br />\n不惜一切代價<br />\n所以終點幾遠 中途有幾多阻礙 身心疲憊都好<br />\n唔好氣餒  僅記一點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不撤不散</span><br />\n同路人上"},{"pid":"130dc6dde5ec9d62cedacdd59723ef6b5ea72cbe","tid":1223972,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:48:02.000Z","msg":"就算失望不能絕望<br />\n 倔強-五月天"},{"pid":"078b66097bc04a86c56a179221245f7167ae769d","tid":1223972,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:48:15.000Z","msg":"大家加油！"},{"pid":"c3da7be86193569e38666a079e0941b7d004db86","tid":1223972,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"130dc6dde5ec9d62cedacdd59723ef6b5ea72cbe","tid":1223972,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:48:02.000Z","msg":"就算失望不能絕望<br />\n 倔強-五月天"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:49:57.000Z","msg":"未到終點絕不能絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd93e991272d91528538519786e5e55c6a33dc08","tid":1223972,"uid":83934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T00:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c230f01504f20806ea1fdcb572c3611c012dd491","tid":1223972,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":